OL,3,CFamily 'forgive' van driver who left
OL,4,Cboy, 7, to die in road 'like an animal'
OL,6,FA van driver who left a young boy to
OL,7,Fdie on a road after hitting him, has
OL,8,Fbeen forgiven by the boy's family on
OL,9,Fthe day of his sentencing.
OL,11,FStewart Powell struck William Brown,
OL,12,F7, as the boy was retrieving his
OL,13,Ffootball from the coast road at
OL,14,FSandgate, Kent in December 2023.
OL,15,FWilliam died at the scene.
OL,17,FPowell, from Dunstall Gardens, St
OL,18,FMary's Bay, pleaded guilty in May to
OL,19,Fleaving the scene of a collision and
OL,20,Fdriving without insurance. The court
OL,21,Fimposed an immediate driving ban.
