OL,3,CFamily 'forgive' van driver who left
OL,4,Cboy, 7, to die in road 'like an animal'
OL,6,FOn 17 July, the 49-year-old was
OL,7,Fsentenced to 14 weeks in prison,
OL,8,Fsuspended for 12 months.
OL,10,FWilliam's parents read statements in
OL,11,Fcourt on the devastating loss of their
OL,12,Fson.
OL,14,FWilliam's mother, Laura Brown, hit out
OL,15,Fat Powell for leaving her son in the
OL,16,Froad "like an animal" and said that he
OL,17,F"deserved better".
