OL,3,CFamily 'forgive' van driver who left
OL,4,Cboy, 7, to die in road 'like an animal'
OL,6,F"Stewart stood watching the
OL,7,Fcatastrophic incident unfold. He made
OL,8,Fa conscious decision to get back into
OL,9,Fhis van and leave him."
OL,11,FShe added: "The not knowing who killed
OL,12,FWilliam tortured my mind. I was
OL,13,Fbegging the van driver to come
OL,14,Fforward. Stewart's actions prolonged
OL,15,Fsuffering we were already enduring."
OL,17,FWilliam Brown Snr said: "It was
OL,18,Fcowardly not to stop and keep driving,
OL,19,FStewart."
