OL,3,CFamily 'forgive' van driver who left
OL,4,Cboy, 7, to die in road 'like an animal'
OL,6,FBut he said: "I know William would
OL,7,Fforgive Stewart... I forgive you
OL,8,FStewart, I give your family peace and
OL,9,Frestoration."
OL,11,FHe added that his son should not have
OL,12,Fbeen in the road, and that the
OL,13,Faccident "could have happened to
OL,14,Fanyone", adding: "I hope we can all
OL,15,Fconsider road safety a priority moving
OL,16,Fforward... so William's life is not
OL,17,Fwasted."
OL,19,FThe court had previously heard that
OL,20,FPowell's van struck William, who was
OL,21,Fthen hit by a second vehicle.
