OL,6,FThe woman driving the second vehicle
OL,7,Fstopped, dialled 999 and stayed with
OL,8,FWilliam.
OL,10,FPowell left the scene and did not
OL,11,Freport the accident until the next
OL,12,Fday, telling police the incident had
OL,13,F"stressed him out".
OL,15,FLater at the police station traces of
OL,16,Fcannabis were found in his system. The
OL,17,Fcourt later heard he was a habitual
OL,18,Fuser of the drug.
