OL,3,CFamily 'forgive' van driver who left
OL,4,Cboy, 7, to die in road 'like an animal'
OL,6,FWilliam's mother, Laura Brown, is
OL,7,Fcampaigning for tougher sentences for
OL,8,Fserious cases of leaving the scene of
OL,9,Fan accident.
OL,11,FShe has started a petition calling for
OL,12,Fa change in the law. The current
OL,13,Fmaximum sentence is six months.
OL,15,FThe petition page reads: "Our lives
OL,16,Fwithout William will never be the
OL,17,Fsame; his small footsteps made a huge
OL,18,Fimpact in this world and has left an
OL,19,Fenormous void in our hearts.
