OL,3,CFamily 'forgive' van driver who left
OL,4,Cboy, 7, to die in road 'like an animal'
OL,6,F"I am petitioning for an amendment of
OL,7,Fthe law. Leaving the scene of an
OL,8,Faccident that law needs to be altered
OL,9,Fto an either way law, which simply
OL,10,Fmeans if you bump someone and drive
OL,11,Foff, you could be dealt with by way of
OL,12,Fa summary or by a Magistrates court,
OL,13,Fif you kill someone in your vehicle
OL,14,Fand leave the scene that should be an
OL,15,Findictable offence that can only be
OL,16,Fdealt with by the Crown Court and
OL,17,Fcould have a maximum of life
OL,18,Fimprisonment."
